{"tid":735693,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救) 第一次見家長一齊食飯，發現碗湯有曱甴","createTime":"2018-07-09T16:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T11:32:43.000Z","uid":194079,"like":123,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b984a1ab509b5e3ee7324fdaef22907c89e6d1","tid":735693,"uid":194079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"話時話小弟今日第一次去女朋友屋企食飯，<br />\n佢哋屋企都好熱情咁招呼我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁飯前會飲一碗湯<br />\n伯母又好熱情咁「buck」咗碗湯俾我飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題嚟啦，係碗湯底我隱隱約約見到一隻曱甴得返半個身體浮下浮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我到底應該飲定唔飲，飲咗又太核突會即刻想嘔，再者佢哋全家人都要飲曱甴湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係如果唔飲，話俾佢哋聽，又好落佢面，會留下不好印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴打你哋話應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n #good         講啦唔講唔通飲咗佢咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />      飲撚咗佢啦 男子漢大丈夫曱甴都唔敢飲？"},{"pid":"b1d5b798e6258dad5c0ee6b58a7f19fdb4f6473a","tid":735693,"uid":156331,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9ef49cb076d78af235b301433dc4b7a11c4163f","tid":735693,"uid":194079,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b1d5b798e6258dad5c0ee6b58a7f19fdb4f6473a","tid":735693,"uid":156331,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"但係有曱甴嘅精華。啲精華喺晒入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cff4207ee18ec1f94c2603751dbe85aa103f29","tid":735693,"uid":146435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a9ef49cb076d78af235b301433dc4b7a11c4163f","tid":735693,"uid":194079,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b1d5b798e6258dad5c0ee6b58a7f19fdb4f6